'''孟噗语'''（[[外名与内名|内名]]：''{{IPA|mɔŋ55 pʰɤ21}}''）是中国[[云南省|云南省]]一种[[缅彝语群|缅彝语群]]，使用在[[广南县|广南县]]八宝镇里洒村<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=258866 |title=广南县八宝镇杨柳树村民委里洒自然村 |access-date=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815164129/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=258866 }}</ref> 和[[富宁县|富宁县]]木央镇值伦村、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=206610 |title=富宁县木央镇木兄坪村委会直伦一村小组 |access-date=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2017-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227070402/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=206610 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=206609 |title=富宁县木央镇木兄坪村委会直伦二村小组 |access-date=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2017-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227121815/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=206609 }}</ref>上者梅村、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=206600 |title=富宁县木央镇木兄坪村委会上者梅村小组 |access-date=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2017-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227121848/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=206600 }}</ref>下者梅村和木杨村。{{Citation needed|有数百名使用者。似乎和普标彝语、麻峨语的亲缘关系最近。|time=2021-04-02}}



